data.text: Yes, and I wanted to go to exam.  I have to take bus for half an hour and I was waiting in the bus stop and the bus just passed me because it was too full.  There were so many people taking the same exam and the bus just passed me and didn't stop.  I was so angry and so worried.  I was afraid to be late for exam because the exam was very important and that was really unpleasant feeling.
